# Staged by mentat-push-server.sh during deploy.
# On mentat-dev, this is a symlink to ../epixodic/score-relay so that
# ecosystem.config.js's relative `score-relay/dist/server.js` path
# resolves locally without duplicating node_modules. Pattern with no
# trailing slash matches both the directory (on nest) and the symlink
# (on mentat).
score-relay
